description:
Sard Super Power, Laundry Stain Remover Refill for Spray, Sard's strongest stain remover spray, Made in Australia, 420ml

Sard Super Power boosted with the power of enzymes is our strongest stain remover spray which tackles not only everyday stains but even tough & dried in stains:
- Red Wine
- Baby Food & Milk
- Blood & Ink
- Sauces & Dressings
- Food

Safe to use on whites and colourfast colours.
We are proudly made in Australia.The Sard bottle and trigger are recyclable.
Sard, Australia's stain expert is tough on stains, gentle on clothes.

Sard Super Power, our strongest spray against even tough & dried in stains

Boosted with the power of enzyme is effective on red wine; baby food & milk; blood & ink; sauces & dressings; food

Safe to use on whites and colourfast colours

Bottle and trigger are recyclable

Made in Australia
